"    Sarcoidosis, stage 2",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 340px; height: 346px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Chest radiograph. Bilateral enlarged hilar lymph nodes as well as right paratracheal and aortopulmonary lymph nodes are visible. Fine linear and reticular opacities are present in the perihilar lung parenchyma.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Courtesy of Paul Stark, MD.",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
